<%- include('./partials/header') %>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-tag">🌍 Our Mission</div>
    <h1>About <em>EduStar</em></h1>
    <p>We believe every African student deserves access to quality education — regardless of where they live or how much money their family has.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="page-section" style="max-width:760px;">
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;margin-bottom:1rem;">Why EduStar exists</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;">Millions of students across Africa study without access to tutors, good textbooks, or learning support. EduStar uses AI to bridge that gap — giving every student a patient, knowledgeable tutor available 24/7, for free.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;margin-bottom:1rem;">What we offer</h2>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);line-height:2;list-style:none;padding:0;">
        <li>🤖 AI Tutor — instant answers to any academic question</li>
        <li>📚 Free textbooks aligned to African curricula</li>
        <li>🌍 Support for 10+ countries and their exam boards</li>
        <li>🏆 Progress tracking and achievement system</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;margin-bottom:1rem;">Supported curricula</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;">ZIMSEC (Zimbabwe) · ECZ (Zambia) · WAEC/NECO (Nigeria) · KCSE/CBC (Kenya) · NECTA (Tanzania) · UNEB (Uganda) · WASSCE (Ghana) · CAPS/NSC (South Africa) · REB (Rwanda)</p>
    </div>
  </div>

